# Shortcuts
Quit all views                  Q
Open view fullscreen            O

# Main
Copy commit hash                H

# Status
Next file                       F
Amend commit                    A
Push                            P
Stage single line               1
Rebase continue                 B
Stage new file                  N
Trash file                      T
Stash (keep index)              S
Graphical diff                  D

# Toggles
Show commit id                  X

# Reflog
tig --reflog

# Other
Screen redraw                   Ctrl-L

# Debug
TIG_TRACE=/tmp/tigtrace tig
